  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Hairstylist",
  "description": "<h3>To apply or find out more, please contact Leong Jia Wei (Reg No: R25157456) at WhatsApp +65 80358497<a href=\"http://wa.me/+6580358497\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://wa.me/+6580358497\"> </a>or email jiawei@placement.com.sg</h3>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong># Experience #</strong></p>\n<p>At least 3 years of haircutting experience in hair salon.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>#Working Conditions#</strong></p>\n<p>5 days work week, outlet opening to closing (earliest from 10am to latest closing 9.30pm)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Note:</p>\n<p>Compulsory training provided upon entry regardless of experience (Minimum 13 days of training depending on skillset)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<p>- Perform haircuts. (No chemical works &amp; shampoo)</p>\n<p>- Provide good customer service</p>\n<p>- Able to consult customers to achieve desired hairstyle</p>\n<p>- Perform cashier duties</p>\n<p>- Maintain cleanliness of outlet</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<p>- Will need to wear uniform during working hours</p>\n<p>- Able to stand for long hours</p>\n<p>- Able to work on weekends &amp; public holidays</p>\n<p>- Service driven</p>\n<p>- Good communication skills</p>\n<p>- Team player</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Salary Package:</strong></u></p>\n<p>Probation period 3 to 6 months</p>\n<p>Welfare Benefits upon confirmation:</p>\n<p>- Medical &amp; Dental $500</p>\n<p>- Annual Variable Bonus</p>\n<p>- Birthday $100</p>\n<p>- Shoes Allowance $100</p>\n<p>- Uniform provided</p>\n<p>- Career Progression</p>\n<p>- Awards &amp; Recognition</p>\n<p>- Fun &amp; Memorable Events</p>",
